title: Header Style 02
layout_xml:
<body>
    <!-- Layout -->
    <referenceContainer name=~~~header.container~~~ htmlClass=~~~page-header header-style-02~~~ />
    <referenceContainer name=~~~header-container-inner~~~>
        <container name=~~~header-sections~~~ htmlId=~~~header-sections~~~ before=~~~-~~~ htmlTag=~~~div~~~ htmlClass=~~~header-sections~~~>
            <container name=~~~header-top~~~ htmlId=~~~header-top~~~ htmlTag=~~~div~~~ htmlClass=~~~header-top~~~ />
            <container name=~~~header-middle~~~ htmlId=~~~header-middle~~~ htmlTag=~~~div~~~ htmlClass=~~~header-middle~~~ />
            <container name=~~~header-bottom~~~ htmlId=~~~header-bottom~~~ after=~~~-~~~ htmlTag=~~~div~~~ htmlClass=~~~header-bottom~~~>
                <container name=~~~header-bottom-container~~~ htmlClass=~~~container~~~ htmlTag=~~~div~~~>
                    <container name=~~~header-bottom-row~~~ htmlClass=~~~row cdz-fix-left menu-area~~~ htmlTag=~~~div~~~>
                        <container name=~~~header-vertical-menu-wrap~~~ htmlTag=~~~div~~~ htmlClass=~~~col-sm-6 header-vertical-menu-wrap no-pad-right~~~ label=~~~Header Vertical Menu~~~ />
                        <container name=~~~header-bottom-right~~~ htmlTag=~~~div~~~ htmlClass=~~~col-sm-24 header-menu-wrap~~~ />
                    </container>
                </container>
            </container>
        </container>
    </referenceContainer>
    
    <referenceContainer name=~~~header.panel~~~>
        <container name=~~~header-panel-container~~~ htmlTag=~~~div~~~ htmlClass=~~~container header-panel-container~~~>
            <container name=~~~header-panel-row~~~ htmlTag=~~~div~~~ htmlClass=~~~header-panel-row row~~~>
                <container name=~~~header-panel-left~~~ htmlTag=~~~div~~~ htmlClass=~~~col-sm-7 header-panel-left~~~ />
                <container name=~~~header-panel-center~~~ htmlTag=~~~div~~~ htmlClass=~~~col-sm-10 header-panel-center header-search-wrap~~~ />
                <container name=~~~header-panel-right~~~ htmlTag=~~~div~~~ htmlClass=~~~col-sm-7 header-panel-right~~~>
                    <container name=~~~header-panel-right-inner~~~ htmlTag=~~~div~~~ htmlClass=~~~header-panel-right-inner~~~ />
                </container>
            </container>
        </container>
    </referenceContainer>
    <move element=~~~header.panel~~~ destination=~~~header-middle~~~ />
    <!-- End Layout -->
    <!-- New Blocks -->
    <block name=~~~header-extra-text-1~~~ class=~~~Codazon\ThemeLayoutPro\Block\Header~~~ template=~~~Codazon_ThemeLayoutPro::layout/header-content.phtml~~~>
        <action method=~~~setData~~~>
            <argument name=~~~name~~~ xsi:type=~~~string~~~>content_type</argument>
            <argument name=~~~value~~~ xsi:type=~~~string~~~>content_1</argument>
        </action>
    </block>
    <block name=~~~header-extra-text-2~~~ class=~~~Codazon\ThemeLayoutPro\Block\Header~~~ template=~~~Codazon_ThemeLayoutPro::layout/header-content.phtml~~~>
        <action method=~~~setData~~~>
            <argument name=~~~name~~~ xsi:type=~~~string~~~>content_type</argument>
            <argument name=~~~value~~~ xsi:type=~~~string~~~>content_2</argument>
        </action>
    </block>
    <block class=~~~Magento\Store\Block\Switcher~~~ name=~~~header-switch-language~~~ template=~~~Magento_Store::switch/languages-style-02.phtml~~~ />
    <block class=~~~Magento\Directory\Block\Currency~~~ name=~~~header-switch-currency~~~ template=~~~Magento_Directory::currency-style-02.phtml~~~ />
    <block class=~~~Magento\Store\Block\Switcher~~~ name=~~~header-switch-store~~~ template=~~~Magento_Store::switch/stores.phtml~~~ />
    <!-- End New Blocks -->
    
    <!-- Top -->
    <move element=~~~header-extra-text-1~~~ destination=~~~header-panel-center~~~ after=~~~-~~~ />
    <move element=~~~header-extra-text-2~~~ destination=~~~header-top~~~ />
    <!-- End Top -->
    
    <!-- Middle -->
    <move element=~~~logo~~~ destination=~~~header-panel-left~~~ before=~~~-~~~ />
    <move element=~~~top.search~~~ destination=~~~header-panel-center~~~ before=~~~-~~~ />
    <move element=~~~mobi-cart-placeholder~~~ destination=~~~header-panel-center~~~ />
    <move element=~~~minicart~~~ destination=~~~header-panel-right-inner~~~ after=~~~-~~~ />
    <move element=~~~top.links.features~~~ destination=~~~header-panel-right-inner~~~ before=~~~-~~~ />
    <referenceBlock name=~~~header-contact-link~~~ remove=~~~true~~~ />
    <move element=~~~minicart~~~ destination=~~~links.features.cart~~~ />
    <move element=~~~links.features.cart~~~ destination=~~~top.links.features~~~ after=~~~authorization-link-features~~~ />
    <!-- End Middle -->

    <!-- Bottom -->
    <move element=~~~catalog.topnav~~~ destination=~~~header-bottom-right~~~ before=~~~-~~~ />
    <move element=~~~store-menu-placeholder~~~ destination=~~~store.menu~~~ />
    <!-- <move element=~~~header-switch-language~~~ destination=~~~header-bottom-right-inner~~~ /> -->
    <!-- <move element=~~~header-switch-currency~~~ destination=~~~header-bottom-right-inner~~~ /> -->
    <move element=~~~store-vertical-menu~~~ destination=~~~header-panel-left~~~ before=~~~-~~~ />
    <!-- End Bottom -->
    <referenceBlock name=~~~utilities.sidebar.right~~~>
        <action method=~~~setData~~~>
            <argument name=~~~name~~~ xsi:type=~~~string~~~>required_blocks</argument>
            <argument name=~~~value~~~ xsi:type=~~~array~~~>
                <item name=~~~getAccountPanelStyle~~~ xsi:type=~~~string~~~>utilities.content</item>
                <item name=~~~getHeaderWishlistStyle~~~ xsi:type=~~~string~~~>wishlist-sidebar</item>
                <item name=~~~getMiniCartStyle~~~ xsi:type=~~~string~~~>minicart-sidebar</item>
            </argument>
        </action>
    </referenceBlock>
    <referenceBlock name=~~~utilities.sidebar.left~~~>
        <action method=~~~setData~~~>
            <argument name=~~~name~~~ xsi:type=~~~string~~~>required_blocks</argument>
            <argument name=~~~value~~~ xsi:type=~~~boolean~~~>0</argument>
        </action>
    </referenceBlock>
    
    <referenceBlock name=~~~top.links~~~>
        <action method=~~~setData~~~>
            <argument name=~~~name~~~ xsi:type=~~~string~~~>css_class</argument>
            <argument name=~~~value~~~ xsi:type=~~~string~~~>header links visible-xs</argument>
        </action>
    </referenceBlock>
</body>

                        <action method=~~~setData~~~>

    <move element=~~~header.panel~~~ destination=~~~header-middle~~~ />

            </arguments>
        </block>
    </referenceContainer>
    <!-- End Top Right -->
    
    <!-- Middle - Left -->
    <move element=~~~logo~~~ destination=~~~header-panel-center~~~ />
    <!-- End Middle - Left -->
    
    <!-- Middle - Center -->
    <move element=~~~mobi-cart-placeholder~~~ destination=~~~header-panel-center~~~ />
    <move element=~~~top.search~~~ destination=~~~header-panel-left~~~ before=~~~-~~~ />
    <!-- End Middle - Center -->
    
    <!-- Middle - Right -->
    <move element=~~~minicart~~~ destination=~~~header-panel-right~~~ after=~~~-~~~ />
    <referenceContainer name=~~~header-panel-right~~~>
        <block name=~~~header-extra-text-2~~~ class=~~~Codazon\ThemeLayoutPro\Block\Header~~~ template=~~~Codazon_ThemeLayoutPro::layout/header-content.phtml~~~>
            <action method=~~~setData~~~>
                <argument name=~~~name~~~ xsi:type=~~~string~~~>content_type</argument>

            </action>

    <referenceBlock name=~~~utilities.sidebar.right~~~>
        <action method=~~~setData~~~>
            <argument name=~~~name~~~ xsi:type=~~~string~~~>required_blocks</argument>
            <argument name=~~~value~~~ xsi:type=~~~array~~~>

    <referenceBlock name=~~~top.links~~~>
        <action method=~~~setData~~~>
            <argument name=~~~name~~~ xsi:type=~~~string~~~>css_class</argument>
            <argument name=~~~value~~~ xsi:type=~~~string~~~>header links visible-xs</argument>
        </action>
    </referenceBlock>
</body>
